Standards-Version: 3.9.1
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7), libkrb5-dev, libldap2-dev, libsasl2-dev, po-debconf (>= 0.5.0), docbook2x, docbook-xml, libpam0g-dev
Homepage: http://arthurdejong.org/nss-pam-ldapd/
